      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;iphone-style-add-a-period-after-entering-two-spaces-in-windows-10&#34;&gt;iPhone style: Add a period after entering two spaces in Windows 10&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;figure markdown&gt;
